import React from 'react'; export default class enterprescription extends React.Component{ constructor(props){ super(props); this.handleChange=this.handleChange.bind(this); this.handleSubmit=this.handleSubmit.bind(this); this.state={ rsign:'0', lsign:'0', resph:0, reax:0, recyl:0, readd:0, lesph:0, leax:0, lecyl:0, leadd:0 } } handleChange(e){ this.props.handleChange(e.target.name,e.target.value); } handleSubmit(e){ this.props.handleSubmit(); } render(){ return (
Sign SPH. CYL. AXIS ADD
RE (0D)
LE (0S)
); } }
